title: Malaysian Economic Indicators: Leading, Coincident & Lagging Indexes August 2015 (DOSM - Department of Statistics ...
text: ( Source : DOSM - Department of Statistics Malaysia ) Highlights The Leading Index (LI) which monitors the economic performance in advance decreased in August 2015 . The LI posted a decrease of 0.9 % to 117 .6 points from 118.7 points in July
